data.description:
MOTIVATED SELLER!  Need space?  Hurry to schedule an appointment to see this home!  A rare opportunity to live in a gated neighborhood off of Hoy Rd.  Conveniently located to downtown Madison shopping and schools.  This over 3800 sq. ft home has an open kitchen including a breakfast area and den with fireplace.  There is an additional living room  with fireplace and formal dining room.  Views of the private backyard can be seen from the living room.  A great place to watch for deer and other wildlife.  The home boast 4 bedrooms and 4 full bathrooms.  Two downstairs and two upstairs.  The upstairs also has a bonus room! The 3 car garage is side entry.  As you visit this home, take note of the ample closet/cabinet/storage space!  
Added features:  In addition to the laundry room which has space for an additional refrigerator, an additional laundry hook-up is located in the main bedroom closet area, a ring security system (also wired for ADT)has been installed, a fort in the back yard adds to the charm, and two water closets in the main bathroom.  If you enjoy entertaining or just need space, come see this home!
